24:00.000 --> 24:04.267
I ran into you at just the right moment.

24:05.267 --> 24:09.200
You rogue, what are you doing
in this part of the world?

24:09.633 --> 24:13.666
And looking so fat and prosperous!

24:13.833 --> 24:16.334
Looks are deceiving!

24:18.100 --> 24:19.433
You're behaving yourself?

24:23.800 --> 24:25.566
But why are you in Seville?

24:27.900 --> 24:30.000
On the Prado,
I saw a flower of beauty.

